Generate 2.0
============
Generate site from static pages, loosely inspired by Jekyll.

Usage
-----
    ./generate.py [options] source_path output_path
Options
    -v activate verbose mode

Dependencies
------------
- [jinja2](http://github.com/mitsuhiko/jinja2) Template language.
- [clint](http://github.com/kennethreitz/clint) Python Command-line Application Tools.

RST templates format should have the following structure:
Context data for jinja template, layout info is required
    {"title": "My awesome site", "layout": "home.html"}
Separator
    ---
Content
    My awesome site content.

